  "texts": [
    "During the review, 18 parameters have been identified.",
    "The parameters used by different researchers in each of the techniques used by load balancing are listed in Table 13.",
    "Studies also focused on providing a load-balancing approach with optimal delay.The QoS metrics considered in the load balancing approaches are grouped into two broad categories; Qualitative metrics and Quantitative metrics.",
    "Also, the metrics may be either dependent or independent.",
    "The taxonomy of the load balancing metrics is shown in Fig. 9.Figure 10 graphically shows the percentage of loadbalancing criteria considered in the articles under review."
  ]
